.el .ds Aq '
.TH link 1  "link " 
.SH NAME
link \- Create and resolve stable syncweb links
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBlink\fR [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] <\fIsubcommands\fR>
.SH DESCRIPTION
Create and resolve stable syncweb links
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
.SH SUBCOMMANDS
.TP
link\-create(1)
Create an immutable, private, or mutable link
.TP
link\-resolve(1)
Resolve a stable link
.TP
link\-revoke(1)
Revoke a private capability link
.TP
link\-help(1)
Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)
